parameters: Do you want to go to the deepest part of the ancient tomb?
Clea (Let's prepare first and then go)

Clea: I'll go in first. Opro-san and Celis-san, please take
care of the rear.
Clea: Also, please take care of this child's protection.

Swift Celis: This time, the one who received the request is
Clea. I intend to follow Clea's judgment.

One-armed Opro: As someone in the position of the client, I
believe Clea's judgment is the best.
Clea: Thank you very much, I'll be going now.

One-armed Opro: She used to be a timid and scared little
girl... It's more than anything to see the growth of young
people at this age.

Swift Celis: I was thinking the same thing. It feels
nostalgic when we first met... That child has come this far.

One-armed Opro: You're too young to tell old stories. You're
a person in the position of creating stories.

Swift Celis: Age doesn't matter when it comes to going on
adventures, Opro-san.

One-armed Opro: I lost an arm... Well, shall we go deeper as
well?
